    <textblock>
      Epidemiology of Helicobacter Pylori Infection Among Shanghai Children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To get an understanding of the Hp infection general situation and provide evidence for Hp
      control, we are planning to run a free physical examination and lab test for a group of
      children. We are going to proceed with Hp-IgG test, 13C urea breath test and salivary Hp urea
      antigen test together to screening and diagnosing it.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
